
Package: cusescrapeR
Title: Access Syracuse MBB Data from Cloudflare R2
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jameson", "Bodenburg", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jameson.bodenburg@gmail.com")
Description: Provides functions to connect to a Cloudflare R2 bucket and
    read play-by-play, box score, game info, stint, roster, and team data
    for Syracuse men's basketball. Requires valid credentials.
